<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

<div class="faq">
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How do I create an account?</h4>
        <p>Click the <a href="@Url.Action("Register","Account")">Register</a> button at the top-right or use the "Start Tracking Now" CTA on the homepage.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How do I add a new plant or resource?</h4>
        <p>After signing in, navigate to the Plant Tracking or Resources section from the left sidebar and use the Add button.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How do I report a bug or request a feature?</h4>
        <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:victor.stefanov.highschool@buditel.bg">victor.stefanov.highschool@buditel.bg</a> with information about the issue or the feature you'd like to see.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<p style="margin-top:18px">Prefer real-time chat? You can also email us and we'll schedule a call or demo.</p>

